### ===========================
### Financials Summary API Tests
### ===========================

@accessToken = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}


### -----------------------------------------------
### Login first (to obtain accessToken)
### -----------------------------------------------
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "Password456!"
}


### ===========================
### Revenue Summary
### ===========================

### 1. Get Monthly Revenue Summary
GET http://localhost:3000/api/revenue-summary?year=2026&month=4
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2. Get Yearly Revenue Summary
GET http://localhost:3000/api/revenue-summary?year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. [Validation] Missing year -> 400
GET http://localhost:3000/api/revenue-summary
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ===========================
### Membership Summary
### ===========================

### 4. Get Membership Summary (monthly)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/membership/summary?year=2026&month=4
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Get Membership Transaction (monthly)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/membership/membership-transaction?year=2026&month=4
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ===========================
### Trainer Expense Summary
### ===========================

### 6. Get Expense Summary (monthly)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trainer-expense/summary?year=2026&month=4
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 7. Get Expense Summary (yearly)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trainer-expense/summary?year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}